B.NG=new A.cc("Lesson 3 \u2014 Entrance Exam Strategy","IOE, IOM, TU, PU \u2014 kasari pass garnu?","Nepal \u092e\u093e \u092e\u0941\u0916\u094d\u092f entrance exams:\n\n1. IOE (Institute of Engineering)\n\u2022 TU Engineering entrance\n\u2022 Physics, Chemistry, Math, English\n\u2022 Cut-off: 60%+ chainchha\n\u2022 Seats: limited \u2014 competition high\n\n2. IOM (Institute of Medicine)\n\u2022 MBBS, BDS, Nursing\n\u2022 Biology, Chemistry, Physics, English\n\u2022 Sabai bhandaa competitive\n\n3. TU/PU Various\n\u2022 BBS, BBA, BCA, BIT\n\u2022 Subject-specific\n\n4. Banking/Finance\n\u2022 NRB, commercial banks\n\u2022 GK + aptitude\n\nEntrance Exam Preparation Strategy:\n\nStep 1: Syllabus download garnu\n\u2022 Official website bata\n\u2022 Topic-wise breakdown garnu\n\u2022 Weightage herna\n\nStep 2: Study material\n\u2022 Recommended books\n\u2022 Past papers \u2014 last 10 years\n\u2022 Online resources\n\nStep 3: Mock tests\n\u2022 Weekly full mock test\n\u2022 Time management practice\n\u2022 Weak areas identify\n\nStep 4: Last 1 month\n\u2022 Revision only\n\u2022 Daily mock test\n\u2022 Physical + mental health\n\nIOE specific tips:\n\u2022 Math \u2014 sabai bhandaa important (40%)\n\u2022 Physics \u2014 conceptual questions\n\u2022 Chemistry \u2014 formulas + reactions\n\u2022 Speed + accuracy duitai chainchha\n\nIOM specific tips:\n\u2022 Biology \u2014 diagrams important\n\u2022 Chemistry \u2014 organic important\n\u2022 MCQ format \u2014 negative marking hunchha\n\nCommon mistakes:\n\u2022 Negative marking bhulinchha\n\u2022 Easy questions skip gardinchha\n\u2022 Time management hudaina\n\u2022 Stress le result bigardichha",B.Zo,"EduPath AI \u0915\u094b Exam Prep section \u092e\u093e \u091c\u093e\u0928\u0941\u0939\u094b\u0938\u094d\u0964 \u0906\u092b\u0941\u0932\u0947 \u0926\u093f\u0928\u0947 entrance exam \u0915\u094b syllabus download \u0917\u0930\u094d\u0928\u0941\u0939\u094b\u0938\u094d\u0964 Topic-wise study plan \u092c\u0928\u093e\u0909\u0928\u0941\u0939\u094b\u0938\u094d\u0964","\u092c\u0941\u091f\u0935\u0932\u0915\u094b \u0938\u0941\u0928\u093f\u0932\u0932\u0947 IOE entrance \u092e\u093e 3rd attempt \u092e\u093e pass \u0917\u0930\u094f\u094b\u0964 \u092a\u0939\u093f\u0932\u094b 2 \u092c\u093e\u0930 Math \u092e\u093e fail \u0925\u093f\u092f\u094b\u0964 3rd attempt \u092e\u093e exclusively Math \u092e\u093e focus \u0917\u0930\u094d\u092f\u094b \u2014 daily 2 \u0918\u0923\u094d\u091f\u093e Math\u0964 Pass \u0917\u0930\u094d\u092f\u094b \u2014 \u0906\u091c TU Engineering \u092e\u093e \u092a\u095d\u094d\u0926\u0948\u091b\u0964")
